{"tid":1379775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線嘅手足, 和理非, 勇武求你哋保護自己 + 重要貼文合集","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:44:25.000Z","uid":164565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57c6fe90ad57a02b6ac813c4d56a236d9751c6c8","tid":1379775,"uid":164565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"728嗰日我哋做錯咗, 分散咗人手, 溝通又不足, 同時無裝備嘅人應該唔好上太前, 唔夠裝備嘅地方唔好守。<br />\n睇片就會發現, 唔夠裝備時喺大馬路守, 被狗一衝, 就有戰友被捕。仲有個錯誤係班狗放完煙, 暴龍即刻衢入嚟打人, 而前線無心理準備去反擊, 最後又有人被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-j9Jd2kl-dY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-j9Jd2kl-dY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyzr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=347edf10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-j9Jd2kl-dY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>不被捕不流血, 每個人都唔可以少</strong><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">齊裝</span>先好上前, 同埋要<span style=\"color: red;\">有心理準備D狗會衝嚟襲擊你</span>, 唔反擊就會被人捉, 所以<span style=\"color: red;\">要盾</span>要棍唔該問後面嘅人借。<br />\n2. 一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">組隊行動</span>, 要走嗰時<span style=\"color: red;\">拉埋落單嘅人一齊走</span>。點解我哋71咁成功, 係因為行動夠一致, 裝備足。 <br />\n3. 和理非唔該幫手<span style=\"color: red;\">帶盾</span> - 浮板, 行李喼, 膠板, <span style=\"color: red;\">棍</span> - 行山杖, 同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">有重量嘅細小物品</span> - <span style=\"color: red;\">保健鐵球</span>。最好有腰包裝細小物品。班狗癩, 有槍, <span style=\"color: red;\">近距離開槍會死人</span>。只要你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係帶違禁品</span>[/red], 就算被狗逗, 都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會有罪</span>。你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要答狗嘅問題, 無野講</span>, 唔好被狗凶到。毅進狗要搵律政司, 舉證你犯法, 有任何疑點都告唔到你, 前線好需要你嘅物資。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLDTNrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLDTNrS.jpg&h=83a68f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 依家D狗有瘋狗症, <span style=\"color: red;\">中意快速衝前開槍同打人</span>, 我地<span style=\"color: red;\">需要大量波子</span>, 阻止D狗衝埋嚟。<span style=\"color: red;\">當D狗準備衝</span>, 除咗玩波子, 仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">要遠攻</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">絕唔可以被狗高速衝擊我地, 今次有好多人就係咁被捉。</span>狗對人係唔會手軟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfwNR01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfwNR01.jpg&h=fef25965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標係形成比較強力嘅防禦陣型, 想走時又安全走到, 想留守時令到D狗無咁易清場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvuDehj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvuDehj.jpg&h=c76c6f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝備篇<br />\n[發夢]晏就好多人冇豬嘴就上咗前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378320/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378320/page/1</a><br />\n[最新防具圖鑑&amp;購買連結] 詳解防具 一齊黎砌史詩裝保家衛港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364591/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364591/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n意見篇<br />\n[前線心態調整] 我係勇武，我覺得衝，都要目標導向，Objective-Oriented<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355/page/1</a><br />\n重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373325/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373325/page/1</a><br />\n [緊急] 你知唔知，場運動就快輸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c6024cc0ac26bd859a85ccfbab6096a28bc9a058","tid":1379775,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"1f506f8028f7a8f6bb12a702ef982d3a5debf9b1","tid":1379775,"uid":164565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45e2f685bc46ca54df4269584271e488bde9e025","tid":1379775,"uid":164565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"